  "Description": {
    "English": "Generalist weapon attachment for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool</span>. Access fire mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> and fire weapon with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-technololy\">Boltcaster</span> reconfigures the Multi-Tool to supercharge <span class=\"name name-earth\">Metallic Elements</span>, firing them as <span class=\"name name-stellar\">high-velocity projectiles</span> capable of causing extreme damage.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具</span>的通用型武器配件。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>进入发射模式，使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>开火。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">离子闪电发射器</span>重新配置的多用途工具可将增压的<span class=\"name name-earth\">金属元素</span>以<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高速射弹</span>的形式射出，并造成巨大伤害。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">工具組</span>的通用武器附加裝置。按 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 進入射擊模式，按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 發射武器。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">雷霆砲</span>會重新設定工具組，讓工具組過量充能<span class=\"name name-earth\">金屬元素</span>，再把這些金屬當成可造成極大傷害的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高速子彈</span>射出。",
    "USEnglish": "Generalist weapon attachment for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool</span>. Access fire mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> and fire weapon with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-technology\">Boltcaster</span> reconfigures the Multi-Tool to supercharge <span class=\"name name-earth\">Metallic Elements</span>, firing them as <span class=\"name name-stellar\">high-velocity projectiles</span> capable of causing extreme damage."
  },
